{
  "id": "RAW_0e763e",
  "title": "GroqCloudTM 开发者层自助访问现已开放 - Groq 提供快速 AI 推理服务",
  "url": "https://groq.com/developer-tier-now-available-on-groqcloud/",
  "date": "2025-02-10 13:18:12",
  "author": "Groq, Inc.",
  "siteName": "Groq",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fbe9ad6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fbe9ad6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aeb0ddb e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"aeb0ddb\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0c8295 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c0c8295\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n       <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’re expanding access to GroqCloud™, ramping up our Developer Tier which is a self-serve access point (or upgrade if you’ve been using our Free Tier up until now). It’s easy – now anyone with a credit card can <a href=\"https://console.groq.com/settings/billing\">sign up</a> for our Developer Tier to pay-as-you-go, getting on-demand access to GroqCloud™. Here are some of the key benefits of joining our Developer Tier.</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24d26c9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"24d26c9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n       <a href=\"https://console.groq.com/settings/billing\"> <picture fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5972\">\n         <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-1024x514.png.webp 1024w, https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-300x150.png.webp 300w, https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-768x385.png.webp 768w, https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1.png.webp 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\">\n         <img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-1024x514.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-1024x514.png 1024w, https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-300x150.png 300w, https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1-768x385.png 768w, https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dev-Tier-Blog-post-image-1.png 1296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\">\n        </picture> </a>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6168ce e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d6168ce\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-176f59f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"176f59f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p>Increased Rate Limits</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-681b975 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"681b975\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’re ready to onboard you to fast AI inference that can grow with you. If you’re looking for a rate limit increase, we’ve got you (</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">up to 10x more than the free tier!). Simply </span><a href=\"https://groq.com/self-serve-support/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">let our team know</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> what your needs are and we’ll get you served. </span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fe288e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4fe288e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16ca0cc elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"16ca0cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n       <span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"> </span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48066c2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"48066c2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4bd5968 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4bd5968\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p>Batch API at a 25% Cost Discount&nbsp;</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-caf9025 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"caf9025\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a9431e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4a9431e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Besides the ease of self-serve access, the Developer Tier also unlocks access to the Batch API! The Batch API offers efficient parallel processing for high-volume workloads – submit 1000s of API requests per batch with guaranteed 24-hour processing time at a 25% cost discount compared to our synchronous APIs. Pricing and details on how to get started </span><a href=\"https://console.groq.com/docs/batch\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n      <p>&nbsp;</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ecf986f elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"ecf986f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n       <span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"> </span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d537772 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d537772\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-885d87f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"885d87f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p>Flex Tier Beta Access</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0136639 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0136639\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our </span><a href=\"https://console.groq.com/docs/service-tiers\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flex Tier</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is now available in beta for all paid customers. It offers on-demand processing when capacity is available, with rapid timeouts if resources are constrained. This tier is perfect for workloads that prioritize fast inference and can gracefully handle occasional request failures. Key benefits include:</span></p>\n      <ul>\n       <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10x rate limits compared to on-demand rate limits</span></li>\n       <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Available for llama-3.3-70b-versatile and llama-3.1-8b-instant models</span></li>\n       <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pricing remains the same as On-Demand tier during beta</span></li>\n      </ul>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4808d6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a4808d6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-496018e elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"496018e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n       <span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"> </span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab45e51 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ab45e51\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9fb88e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c9fb88e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p>Growing Fast?</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d3b87d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8d3b87d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re looking to take your access to the next level, our enterprise solutions are perfect for custom solutions and large scale needs requiring enterprise-grade capacity and dedicated support. Reach out to our team </span><a href=\"https://groq.com/enterprise-access/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> about Enterprise access.&nbsp;</span></p>\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also see our most up to date pricing </span><a href=\"http://groq.com/pricing\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-138e3ea e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"138e3ea\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a1033f elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"1a1033f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n       <span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"> </span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6d7bb9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b6d7bb9\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n   <div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-45cb4df elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"45cb4df\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p>Ready to Build?</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-211ec48 e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"211ec48\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a4829b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2a4829b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n       <p><a href=\"https://console.groq.com/keys\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create your free API</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> key and move seamlessly to Groq from other providers like OpenAI by changing three lines of code:</span></p>\n       <ol>\n        <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With our OpenAI endpoint compatibility, simply set </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">OPENAI_API_KEY</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to your Groq API Key.</span></li>\n        <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Set the base URL.</span></li>\n        <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose your model and run!</span></li>\n       </ol>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe4afb1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fe4afb1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n       <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://groq.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/openai_to_groq-square-10s-rectangle.gif\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-4451\" alt=\"\">\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2cb8daf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2cb8daf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n     <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose from popular text and audio models like </span><a href=\"https://groq.com/the-crucial-role-of-context-length-in-large-language-models-for-business-applications/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DeepSeek R1 Distill Llama 70B</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">,&nbsp; </span><a href=\"https://console.groq.com/playground?model=llama-3.3-70b-versatile\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Llama 3.3 70B</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and </span><a href=\"https://console.groq.com/playground?model=whisper-large-v3\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whisper Large v3</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Here are a few other resources our devs love:</span></p>\n      <ul>\n       <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ig7esRBhFPY\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Getting Started Video</span></a></li>\n       <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://console.groq.com/docs/quickstart\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quickstart Guide</span></a></li>\n       <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://github.com/groq/groq-api-cookbook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Groq API Cookbook</span></a></li>\n      </ul>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Groq 推出 GroqCloudTM 开发者层，提供自助访问、更高速率限制和批量 API，旨在提供更快速、经济的 AI 推理服务。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Groq 推出 GroqCloudTM 开发者层，提供自助访问、更高速率限制和批量 API，旨在提供更快速、经济的 AI 推理服务。",
  "summary": "Groq 宣布扩展 GroqCloudTM 的访问权限，推出开发者层，允许用户按需付费使用 GroqCloudTM。开发者层的主要优势包括更高的速率限制 (比免费层高 10 倍)，以及批量 API 的访问权限，批量 API 提供高效并行处理，成本降低 25%。此外，所有付费客户现在都可以使用 Flex Tier 的 Beta 版本，该版本在容量可用时提供按需处理，如果资源受限，则请求可能会快速超时。Groq 还提供企业解决方案，以满足需要企业级容量和专门支持的定制解决方案和大规模需求。Groq 提供 OpenAI 端点兼容性，简化了从其他提供商 (如 OpenAI) 的迁移。只需更改三行代码即可完成迁移。Groq 提供的模型选择包括 Llama 3 和 Whisper。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "开发者可以自助访问 GroqCloud，按需使用，更加灵活。",
      "explanation": "开发者可以通过信用卡注册开发者层，根据使用情况付费，并按需访问 GroqCloudTM。"
    },
    {
      "point": "批量 API 提供高效的并行处理，并降低成本。",
      "explanation": "批量 API 允许每个批次提交数千个 API 请求，保证 24 小时处理时间，成本比同步 API 降低 25%。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Flex Tier Beta 为付费客户提供具有快速推理的按需处理。",
      "explanation": "Flex Tier 在容量可用时提供按需处理，速率限制比按需模式高 10 倍。但如果资源受限，请求可能会快速超时，适用于优先考虑快速推理的工作负载。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "批量 API 为高容量工作负载提供高效的并行处理——每个批次可以提交数千个 API 请求，保证 24 小时处理时间，并且成本比同步 API 降低 25%。(英文原文: The Batch API offers efficient parallel processing for high-volume workloads -- submit 1000s of API requests per batch with guaranteed 24-hour processing time at a 25% cost discount compared to our synchronous APIs.)",
    "我们的 Flex Tier 现已面向所有付费客户推出 Beta 版本。它在容量可用时提供按需处理，如果资源受限，请求可能会快速超时。(英文原文: Our Flex Tier is now available in beta for all paid customers. It offers on-demand processing when capacity is available， with rapid timeouts if resources are constrained.)",
    "只需更改三行代码即可从 OpenAI 迁移到 Groq。(英文原文: 只需更改三行代码即可从 OpenAI 迁移到 Groq)"
  ],
